   <sec>
    <title>
     Cellular function of the Vps23 type II site
    </title>
    <p>
     ESCRT-I is predominantly cytosolic in both wild-type and the type II site mutant
     <em>
      VPS23
     </em>
     <sup>
      <em>
       W16A
      </em>
     </sup>
     (
     <xref ref-type="fig">
